com.vmware.nsx_vmc_app.infra

Class InfraFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_vmc_app.infra.InfraFactory

  • public class InfraFactory
extends Object
    InfraFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_vmc_app.infra package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
